description:
John Durham’s latest report reveals hundreds of emails between Fusion GPS and reporters. All of this as Twitter’s board of directors accepts Elon Musk’s $44 billion offer to buy Twitter, and new video footage shows Alec Baldwin pointing a gun at the camera on ‘Rust’ set. Meanwhile, a federal judge temporarily blocks the Biden administration from lifting Title 42 COVID-19 border restrictions for migrants, and 22-year old National Guardsman, Bishop Evans tragically loses his life while trying to rescue drug-smugglers.
